Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.48,0:00:06.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Edolas's King Faust ordered the merciless \Nannihilation of all in his way.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.98,0:00:14.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy, Gray, and the members of Edolas's \NFairy Tail all stood up against the Royal Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.82,0:00:19.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The three Dragon Slayers, \NNatsu, Gajeel, and Wendy,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.05,0:00:25.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,battle Droma Anim, a hardened \Narmor that Faust is piloting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.86,0:02:08.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wizards of Earthland!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.11,0:02:13.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who possess within them an eternal, \Nnever-ending supply of magic power...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.45,0:02:20.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And among them, you Dragon Wizards \Nand your ridiculous magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.40,0:02:26.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hand your magic power over \Nto me! This world demands it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.73,0:02:34.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fall down to earth, dragons!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.86,0:02:46.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as we have this ultimate magic \Nweapon, Droma Anim, our army will never be destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.77,0:03:00.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Getting up again?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.92,0:03:03.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Impressive...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.06,0:03:05.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That magic power is incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.91,0:03:09.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dragon Wizards, you will be ours!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.39,0:03:19.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Standing Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.57,0:03:37.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Collect more magic power!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.14,0:03:42.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Droma Anim, collect magic power \Nfrom the sky and the land!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.46,0:03:57.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can feel it... This world is \Nrunning out of magic power...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.49,0:04:03.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And that is precisely why you must be ours!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.59,0:04:08.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Salamander, use your breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.76,0:04:10.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You too, brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.79,0:04:12.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All three at the same time?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.74,0:04:16.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want to suggest it 'cause \NI'm not sure what'll happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.31,0:04:18.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But we got no choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.61,0:04:19.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.98,0:04:21.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.56,0:04:25.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Roar of the...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.84,0:04:26.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Roar of the...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.98,0:04:28.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Roar of the...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.42,0:04:32.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Their magic power is rising again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.95,0:04:35.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.95,0:04:35.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Iron Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.95,0:04:35.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sky Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.02,0:04:55.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did that do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.15,0:05:01.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Above!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.57,0:05:08.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It could jump that high?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.82,0:05:12.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! Our triple roar didn't hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.58,0:05:14.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll do it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.08,0:05:16.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't get a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.44,0:05:20.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dragon Knight Spread Cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.14,0:05:39.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For the world... For our Edolas...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.23,0:05:43.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the difference between you and I.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.81,0:05:48.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You said that you didn't know anything \Nabout this world, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.42,0:05:55.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the living creatures of this world \Nrequire aren't guilds... It's eternal magic power!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.65,0:05:58.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's required by the citizens.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.20,0:06:04.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have any of the \Nburden of responsibility!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.59,0:06:14.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad... My magic power is... almost...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.35,0:06:16.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you're running on empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.43,0:06:34.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how infinite it may be, it takes \Ntime to regenerate once used up, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.22,0:06:39.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now don't struggle, and become \Nthe magic power of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.17,0:06:45.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How well you are treated will \Ndepend on your attitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.18,0:06:50.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use... I can't stand up...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.51,0:06:52.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the end?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.57,0:06:58.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.43,0:07:03.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It ain't over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.02,0:07:07.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.08,0:07:10.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm standin' right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.01,0:07:15.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You are one obstinate brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.20,0:07:19.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.95,0:07:24.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool... What can you do \Nwithout any magic power?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.21,0:07:25.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I squeeze it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.30,0:07:28.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.74,0:07:35.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I squeeze it out from tomorrow's!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.23,0:07:48.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate a Dragon Slayer!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.32,0:07:53.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,From... tomorrow's?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.56,0:07:57.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll beat it into you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.20,0:08:04.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll learn just who I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.98,0:08:07.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.04,0:08:09.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need to combine our powers!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.91,0:08:14.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All we need is our power, \Nour wishes, to be as one!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.11,0:08:17.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My foot...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.97,0:08:21.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Locked down! Now you can't \Nescape into the air!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.17,0:08:25.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.84,0:08:28.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Salamander!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.37,0:08:30.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's got to be you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.41,0:08:32.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.52,0:08:37.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wendy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.95,0:08:41.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Roar towards me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.29,0:08:43.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand up!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.54,0:08:45.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.00,0:08:47.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe in you, Natsu-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.82,0:08:52.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You stubborn little... Get off!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.32,0:08:54.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Never, you pile of scrap!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.68,0:09:10.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Roar of the... Sky Dragon!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.12,0:09:21.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it... Use the special \Nvortex of her breath, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.73,0:09:38.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this... a fantasy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.97,0:09:43.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sword Edge of the Fire Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.71,0:10:40.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is... Is this what I desired?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.51,0:11:02.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Save me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.86,0:11:25.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We defeated the King!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.26,0:11:27.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you call that again? Checkmate?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.81,0:11:31.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're supposed to say that \N{\i1}before{\i0} you capture the king!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.09,0:11:33.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.66,0:11:37.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.25,0:11:39.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Reinforcements?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.18,0:11:43.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've gotta be kiddin' me... I'm \N{\i1}really{\i0} out of magic power now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.74,0:11:46.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not... It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.60,0:11:53.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The floating islands are falling.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.26,0:12:17.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this? The islands in the sky are...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.88,0:12:20.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, whoa! What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.29,0:12:23.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're in big trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.39,0:12:29.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.00,0:12:34.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The floating islands of Edolas work \Nusing the world's magic power.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.20,0:12:37.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So if they are falling, that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.57,0:12:42.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The magic is disappearing from this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.72,0:12:48.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.66,0:12:51.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know... But, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.63,0:12:58.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is... magic power?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.42,0:13:00.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is this happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.65,0:13:21.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The time has finally come...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.52,0:13:22.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Byro!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.65,0:13:26.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.36,0:13:29.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.00,0:13:31.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty? What do you mean, Sugar Boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.83,0:13:33.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean the magic power...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.95,0:13:40.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I expected flowing magic \Npower to be more... fearsome.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.35,0:13:46.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Prince...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.28,0:13:48.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.14,0:13:52.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as there is magic power, \Npeople will fight over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.79,0:13:56.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore I will rid this \Nworld of magic completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.12,0:14:04.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Anima I have set in reverse will flow \Nall the magic power from Edolas to Earthland.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.92,0:14:07.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In Earthland, already overflowing with magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.26,0:14:10.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,this magic power will quickly be \Ntransformed into a part of nature there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.45,0:14:17.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,To create a new world, I will \Ndestroy a portion of Edolas.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.11,0:14:26.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't use my weapon any more!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.31,0:14:27.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.76,0:14:29.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Same over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.91,0:14:31.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What'll we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.34,0:14:33.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My weapon's broken!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.95,0:14:40.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.98,0:14:43.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My weapon! My weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.73,0:14:45.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.16,0:14:49.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's over... The world is ending...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.01,0:14:51.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Carla...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.01,0:15:01.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's magic power!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.04,0:15:02.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic power?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.37,0:15:05.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Won't losing all the magic \Npower be a big problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.56,0:15:19.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.14,0:15:22.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If we can't use our weapons, we're screwed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.03,0:15:24.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Royal Army's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.38,0:15:25.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.09,0:15:28.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey guys, we did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.43,0:15:32.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.46,0:15:36.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic power is disappearing... \NWe can't use magic anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.20,0:15:38.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is coming to an end...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.83,0:15:40.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, today is the day...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.14,0:15:41.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.59,0:15:44.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going to happen to us? To the guild?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.94,0:15:49.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no such thing as a wizard's \Nguild that can't use magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.59,0:15:52.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone calm down! It'll be okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.87,0:15:54.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Like hell it will!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.51,0:15:58.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The magic power is disappearing \Nfrom the world! All of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.33,0:16:00.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's gonna happen to our wizard guild?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.93,0:16:06.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's over... We may have won the \Nbattle, but we lost the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.82,0:16:11.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The thing Juvia feared most of \Nall... Magic power drying up...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.76,0:16:16.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic is vanishing! Magic \Npower is disappearing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.72,0:16:18.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.59,0:16:19.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Save us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.97,0:16:21.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What'll we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.74,0:16:23.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the end of the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.51,0:16:25.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Edolas's final day...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.89,0:16:27.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.65,0:16:34.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe it... Magic \Npower is vanishing from Edolas.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.59,0:16:37.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is coming to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.46,0:16:57.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad... All the floating \Nislands are falling...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.37,0:16:59.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all over...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.44,0:17:07.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where do they think they're running?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.92,0:17:11.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,To us, Edolas is everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.95,0:17:19.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic power is flowing from \Nthe land into the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.30,0:17:20.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.51,0:17:24.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this punishment for opposing the Exceed?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.15,0:17:27.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's started.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.48,0:17:29.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing's started.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.65,0:17:30.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.39,0:17:33.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Edolas is finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.30,0:17:37.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's happening so simply...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.83,0:17:42.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Royal City, Edolas... \NHistory itself is ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.87,0:17:47.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you even imagine a world without magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.24,0:17:52.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know... I haven't \Never thought about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.72,0:17:59.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not just us... Can the people \Nin town imagine it themselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.98,0:18:15.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma, watch out! The rivers \Nin the sky are falling!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.71,0:18:18.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The world is finished...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.05,0:18:20.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's head back to the \Ncity around the castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.82,0:18:22.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you planning to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.47,0:18:24.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm worried about the people in the city!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.66,0:18:28.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There might be something that we can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.03,0:18:31.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... I think I understand what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.70,0:18:32.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.40,0:18:36.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.68,0:18:46.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this world finished?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.65,0:18:54.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you really did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.44,0:18:58.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.15,0:19:03.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know... The citizens will be in a panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.58,0:19:09.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not many humans can adapt so \Nquickly to a changing world...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.13,0:19:21.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My fire lacrima broke!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.14,0:19:25.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why they need a new leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.83,0:19:29.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A new king for a new world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.93,0:19:34.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,To soothe the unease of the citizens,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.91,0:19:36.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and lead them to happiness...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.54,0:19:37.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A new king.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.86,0:19:40.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. And it will be you, Prince?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.67,0:19:43.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No. Not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.12,0:19:47.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That would not be possible for me, \Nwho did not walk with this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.36,0:19:50.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, I have no right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.97,0:19:57.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,To calm the rioting masses, we need someone \Nto play both the hero, and the villain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.17,0:20:00.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Villain and hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.85,0:20:06.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who exposes and punishes the villain
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.05,0:20:08.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,who plunged the world into \Nchaos will become a hero,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.79,0:20:11.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and that hero will unite the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.67,0:20:14.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll become king.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.18,0:20:20.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! The water lacrima disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.10,0:20:21.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Same with the fire lacrima in my house!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.78,0:20:23.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My vehicle won't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.57,0:20:25.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The wind lacrima isn't working!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.74,0:20:27.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.05,0:20:28.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.28,0:20:33.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Who will be the villain and the hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.66,0:20:35.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You already know that, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.33,0:20:42.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the evil villain who overthrew the king \Nand stole the magic power from this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.33,0:20:47.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And you are suited to heal \Nthe misunderstandings
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.29,0:20:49.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and prejudice between the races...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.50,0:20:54.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You will execute me, the one \Nwho destroyed the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.27,0:20:58.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And then you will become the world's king!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.31,0:21:07.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,God, please save us!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.69,0:21:20.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you! This isn't time to be taking notes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.08,0:21:24.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We are now standing up against \Nthe end of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.10,0:21:28.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As a living being of Edolas, I \Nmust record all that happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.43,0:21:29.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Suit yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.09,0:21:43.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You must execute me, the one who caused this \Nturmoil, in front of the panicking citizens.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.73,0:21:48.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As a member of the Royal \NArmy... As an Exceed...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.47,0:21:52.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Quell the panic, and lead the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.27,0:21:58.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Become King of a new world, \Nwithout magic power.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.33,0:22:19.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you seriously say \Nsuch nonsense, Prince?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.98,0:23:59.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What'll happen to this world when \Nall the magic power is gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.28,0:24:00.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't imagine it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.98,0:24:05.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a world unlike ours, where \Neverything revolves around magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.38,0:24:08.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But what's most important \Nisn't magic power, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.25,0:24:13.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't what's most important the friends \Nthat help and believe in each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.88,0:24:16.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: Bye-bye, Edolas.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.27,0:24:19.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes even you have \Na way with words, Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.89,0:24:22.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a jab in there, wasn't there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.18,0:24:24.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all. I was complimenting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.52,0:24:26.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,
